Uses of Package
io.atomix

  • Packages that use io.atomix 
    Package Description
    io.atomix
    Core Atomix APIs, including ResourceClient and io.atomix.manager.ResourceReplica.
  • Classes in io.atomix used by io.atomix 
    Class and Description
    Atomix
    Base type for creating and managing distributed resources in a Atomix cluster.
    AtomixClient
    Provides an interface for creating and operating on Resources remotely.
    AtomixClient.Builder
    Builds an AtomixClient.
    AtomixProperties
    Base class for Atomix properties.
    AtomixReplica
    Provides an interface for creating and operating on Resources as a stateful node.
    AtomixReplica.Builder
    Builds an AtomixReplica.
